<subSubSection id="20A5654A5173725D18CEFB5BD4D7FB3B" pageId="16" pageNumber="53" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="680036C15173725D18CEFB5BD4D7FB3B" blockId="16.[151,1437,151,1400]" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">
<emphasis id="5ACBEAD35173725D18CEFB5BD142FB17" bold="true" box="[199,334,1196,1221]" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">Etymology.</emphasis>
From a combination of the species name “ 
<taxonomicName id="AFBF4D425173725D1B34FB5BD361FB16" baseAuthorityName="Duda" baseAuthorityYear="1924" box="[829,877,1196,1220]" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Lordiphosa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="miki">
<emphasis id="5ACBEAD35173725D1B34FB5BD361FB16" box="[829,877,1196,1220]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">miki</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” and Greek word “oides” (meaning “resembling 
<taxonomicName id="AFBF4D425173725D189EFB27D0CBFB3A" baseAuthorityName="Duda" baseAuthorityYear="1924" box="[151,199,1232,1256]" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Lordiphosa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="miki">
<emphasis id="5ACBEAD35173725D189EFB27D0CBFB3A" box="[151,199,1232,1256]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">miki</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”), referring to the large, longitudinal row of sex-comb resembling those in the 
<taxonomicName id="AFBF4D425173725D1C37FB26D487FB3A" baseAuthorityName="Duda" baseAuthorityYear="1924" box="[1086,1163,1232,1256]" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Lordiphosa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="miki">
<emphasis id="5ACBEAD35173725D1C37FB26D441FB3A" box="[1086,1101,1233,1256]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">L</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="5ACBEAD35173725D1C52FB27D487FB3A" box="[1115,1163,1232,1256]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">miki</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
