<subSubSection id="20A5654A5173725D18CEFAE0D174FAAA" pageId="16" pageNumber="53" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="680036C15173725D18CEFAE0D174FAAA" blockId="16.[151,1437,151,1400]" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">
<emphasis id="5ACBEAD35173725D18CEFAE0D137FAE2" bold="true" box="[199,315,1303,1328]" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species clearly belongs to the 
<taxonomicName id="AFBF4D425173725D1AE4FAEED376FAE2" baseAuthorityName="Okada &amp; Sasakawa" baseAuthorityYear="1956" box="[749,890,1304,1328]" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Lordiphosa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="denticeps">
<emphasis id="5ACBEAD35173725D1AE4FAEED376FAE2" box="[749,890,1304,1328]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">L. denticeps</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group in light of the diagnosis, but has quite particular sex-combs, which are also seen in the succeeding two new species, 
<taxonomicName id="AFBF4D425173725D1C5FFACAD4DEFA86" authority="Katoh &amp; Zhang &amp; Toda &amp; Zhang &amp; Gao, 2018" authorityName="Katoh &amp; Zhang &amp; Toda &amp; Zhang &amp; Gao" authorityYear="2018" box="[1110,1234,1340,1364]" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Lordiphosa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kimurai" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="5ACBEAD35173725D1C5FFACAD4DEFA86" box="[1110,1234,1340,1364]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">L. kimurai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="41F857A85173725D1CE9FACBD54CFA87" box="[1248,1344,1340,1365]" pageId="16" pageNumber="53" rank="species">
<emphasis id="5ACBEAD35173725D1CE9FACBD54CFA87" bold="true" box="[1248,1344,1340,1365]" pageId="16" pageNumber="53">sp. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName id="AFBF4D425173725D1D8CFACAD114FAAA" authority="Katoh &amp; Zhang &amp; Toda &amp; Zhang &amp; Gao, 2018" authorityName="Katoh &amp; Zhang &amp; Toda &amp; Zhang &amp; Gao" authorityYear="2018" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Lordiphosa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anthophilia" status="sp. nov.">
